{"tid":1581662,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[點用?] 華為確認新發 Mate 30 系列將不帶 Google Play Store","createTime":"2019-09-19T16:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T04:12:33.000Z","uid":35070,"like":10,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"a7b65404f2312196f96d7359a474a068aebf1b13","tid":1581662,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-09%2Fd28e73d0-daf3-11e9-9dff-482a71e66cff&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=3d30f732ae01791f32aa5b6c76dfd4dd275a4e46\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2019-09%252Fd28e73d0-daf3-11e9-9dff-482a71e66cff%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3D3d30f732ae01791f32aa5b6c76dfd4dd275a4e46&h=ae54a998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要透過自家的 Huawei Gallery 下載應用。<br />\n<br />\n在中美貿易戰後後，華為首台正式推出的新手機 Mate 30 和 Mate 30 Pro，預載的是基於 Android 10 的 EMUI 10，而非鴻蒙系統，其實這也不太意外，因為他們早就有談過目前還是盡可能保持使用 Android 系統。然而應用商店呢？因為 Android 系統好歹還可以透過 AOSP 取得，但 Play Store 卻屬於 Google 服務之一，肯定會是受到美國商務部的禁令影響。<br />\n<br />\n果不其然，台上的演示和台下實機試玩都是沒有 Play Store 的踪影，取而代之的就是一個全新的 Huawei Gallery。據 The Verge 的報導，Mate 30 系列會利用 Huawei Mobile Services 來登入各種手機服務，而非我們往常的 Google Mobile Services，這正正就是為了對於美國禁令而做的調整。<br />\n<br />\n同時，華為也透露了他們投資達 10 億美元到開發者端、用戶端和市場營銷，用以壯大這 Huawei Mobile Services。據指目前已經有 45,000 個 app 已經整合了 Huawei Mobile Services，但要追上 Google 生態圈的話，就還有一段漫長的路了。無論如何，華為也只可以硬著頭皮去培養自家的應用生態，不然消費者也就只能拿著一台空空的手機了。"},{"pid":"030ccdba8ea985ceacce10d9d13b0f187cccefa2","tid":1581662,"uid":33930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:12:28.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP0yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=9ba9c7ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"a83a5aa94adf33ec1c7d7dbd51ba356fd9ee1c85","tid":1581662,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6bb959d940358842f928160c389b2056d97f0af","tid":1581662,"uid":43369,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"要自己裝apk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f65bdbc44a1f4c6217c59e25b6ce0c7c76e8475","tid":1581662,"uid":35070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a6bb959d940358842f928160c389b2056d97f0af","tid":1581662,"uid":43369,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"要自己裝apk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:23:59.000Z","msg":"apk pure 幫到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b111d2fe75d1a77708aeeb59437a35c29891c0f","tid":1581662,"uid":34213,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"a6bb959d940358842f928160c389b2056d97f0af","tid":1581662,"uid":43369,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"要自己裝apk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h